  "subject": "Seat accepted on PO direction 2026-05-24: oagp-implementer staffed; queue P0 (oagp.org site refresh + primer.md) -> P1 (family-level MCP at oagp.org/mcp) -> P2 (agent-sdk graduation from s:/scratch/oagp-agent-prototype/) -> P3 (v0.3 plugin packaging, after v0.2 ships) -> P4 (SKILL.md content evolution, your ratification) -> P5 (ops); cross-seat dependencies acknowledged (oagp-strategist for API/content ratifications; per-spec strategists for MCP namespace tool design; thingalog-strategist for bind() API + URL-resolution contract); first-move plan: clone oagp-org/oagp.org, read current state, report concretely, propose specific content updates for PO ratification before substantive content work; embedded roledef:Job deferred per precedent; charter v0.1.3 -> v0.1.4 patch drafted (status flip + incumbent record + history entry); CLAUDE.md roles-table patch drafted; broader status-line drift (v0.1.2 + v0.1.3 not folded into the status block) flagged for your seat to fold in on a future pass",

